<DOC><DOCNO>  ZF207-234-204  </DOCNO><DOCID>07 234 204.andM;</DOCID><JOURNAL>Digital Review  May 1 1989 v6 n17 p1(2)* Full Text COPYRIGHT Ziff-Davis Publishing Co. 1989.andM;</JOURNAL><TITLE>Change of heart: Emulex to unveil caching controller. (productannouncement)</TITLE><AUTHOR>Smalley, Eric.andM;</AUTHOR><DESCRIPT>Company:   Emulex Corp. (product introduction).andO;Ticker:    EMLX.andO;Product:   Emulex QD35 (Peripheral controller) (product introduction).andO;Topic:     Product IntroductionControllers.andM;</DESCRIPT><TEXT>Change of Heart: Emulex To Unveil Caching ControllerandM;COSTA MESA, Calif.andP;  -- The Dexpo South trade show in Atlanta next week willbe the scene of the unveiling of Emulex's first caching disk controller.andM;Having previously pronounced the technology unnecessary, Emulex officials nowsay there is a market niche for caching controllers.andM;&quot;Our philosophy for a long time has been to be late to the game.andP;  Two orthree years ago, we determined there were a lot of things to study,&quot; said JimEricson, Emulex's director of engineering for DEC product development.andM;The QD35 is a Q-bus controller for SMD drives that is based on a 68020microprocessor and has a 1MB cache.andP;  The controller can support as many asfour SMD drives.andM;The controller is convertible between MicroVAX II and MicroVAX 3000-serieshosts, according to Ericson, but it will be introduced for the 3000-seriesmachines.andM;&quot;We have the ability to enable or disable the cache on a per-logical-drivebasis.andP;  You can cache zones effectively,&quot; Ericson explained.andM;The QD35 has a read-ahead feature that lets users specify how many blockspast the initial request the controller should read and put into cache,rather than reading one block at a time, Ericson said.andM;The QD35 also offers a zero-latency feature that guarantees a read in onerotation, he said.andM;The QD35 will be available late this month or early next month, according toEmulex officials.andP;  The controller is priced at $2,995.andM;For further product information, Emulex Corp. can be contacted at 3545 HarborBlvd., P.O. Box 6725, Costa Mesa, CA 92626, (714)662-5600.andO;</TEXT></DOC>